  #250134).  Artifact from ebuild update alertly noticed by SpanKY.

  23 Oct 2008; Steve Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org> gpsdrive-2.10_pre5.ebuild:
  Updated with fix for bug #238959 and mysql example config.

